{"type": "article", "id": 29, "title": "世界杯要来了，喜力先给你点好看的", "description": "世界杯要来了，喜力先给你点好看的", "date": "2014-04-28T20:31:32Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 12, "column": null, "author": 2, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052027419LUt1lcICRTWpGNf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t一张画着喜力酒瓶的白纸能变成什么？喜力邀请 40 位传奇人物创作了名为一组<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/art/heineken-the-legendary-posters-04-15-2014/\" target=\"_blank\">“传奇海报”</a>，以支持<a href=\"https://en.rsf.org/\" target=\"_blank\">记者无国界</a>组织。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t你可以看到一些非常夸张的作品，比如网球明星 Jimmy Connors 身着防火服，将一个燃烧着的网球击向海报：\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"http://121.201.7.32:8001/uploads/image/201404/da9a5ab10a9d.gif\" alt=\"\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t或者一位自由潜水潜入 60 米深度在海报上写下自己的名字\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"http://121.201.7.32:8001/uploads/image/201404/0cd2ec3142c2.gif\" alt=\"\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t更多海报见 <a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/art/heineken-the-legendary-posters-04-15-2014/\">DesignBoom</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/art/heineken-the-legendary-posters-04-15-2014/\"></a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}